- Kept the existing `/system/components/dashboards/:componentId` route as the single `system-component-dashboards` registration because Vue Router was already resolving the duplicate name to that route, and `ComponentsView` depends on `route.params.componentId` to open the drawer.
- Treated `null` API list payloads the same as empty arrays only after the view's loading ref is false, preserving the current loading behavior while fixing blank System tabs for empty SSP implementations.
- Left the shared `src/components/system-security-plans/` create/edit forms untouched; only their dialog call sites and list append behavior were adjusted so the SSP-area refactor can own form validation and markup.
- Replaced Overview progress bars with neutral bordered stat cards plus text summaries instead of introducing a shared stat component, keeping the cleanup local to the System overview and preserving all displayed compliance values.
- Swallowed 404s only for optional diagram group fetches, while leaving non-404 diagram fetch failures to reject as before.

